name: Ecs

values.name: clear
values.comment: Remove all components of an entity.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.Spec comparable ecs -> comparable -> ecs -> ecs

values.name: componentCount
values.comment: Determine the total number of components in the ecs.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.Spec comparable ecs -> ecs -> Basics.Int

values.name: empty
values.comment: Create an empty ecs.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.Spec comparable ecs -> ecs

values.name: entityCount
values.comment:
Determine the total number of entities in the ecs.
Warning: this is an expensive operation.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.Spec comparable ecs -> ecs -> Basics.Int

values.name: get
values.comment: Get a specific component of an entity.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.ComponentSpec comparable ecs a -> comparable -> ecs -> Maybe.Maybe a

values.name: has
values.comment: Determines if an entity has a specific component.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.ComponentSpec comparable ecs a -> comparable -> ecs -> Basics.Bool

values.name: ids
values.comment:
Get all entity ids in the ecs.
Warning: this is an expensive operation.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.Spec comparable ecs -> ecs -> Set.Set comparable

values.name: insert
values.comment: Insert a specific component in an entity.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.ComponentSpec comparable ecs a -> comparable -> a -> ecs -> ecs

values.name: isEmpty
values.comment: Determine if the ecs is empty
values.type: Ecs.Internal.Spec comparable ecs -> ecs -> Basics.Bool

values.name: member
values.comment: Determine if an entity is in the ecs.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.Spec comparable ecs -> comparable -> ecs -> Basics.Bool

values.name: remove
values.comment: Remove a specific component from an entity.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.ComponentSpec comparable ecs a -> comparable -> ecs -> ecs

values.name: select
values.comment: Get a specific set of components of an entity.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.Selector comparable ecs a -> comparable -> ecs -> Maybe.Maybe a

values.name: selectList
values.comment: Get all entities with a specific set of components.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.Selector comparable ecs a -> ecs -> List.List ( comparable, a )

values.name: size
values.comment: Determine the total number of components of a specific type.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.ComponentSpec comparable ecs a -> ecs -> Basics.Int

values.name: update
values.comment: Update a specific component in an entity.
values.type: Ecs.Internal.ComponentSpec comparable ecs a -> comparable -> (Maybe.Maybe a -> Maybe.Maybe a) -> ecs -> ecs

name: Ecs.Select

aliases.name: Selector
aliases.comment: A selector of a specific set of components.

values.name: andFilter
values.comment: Also only keep data that satify the test.

values.comment: Also check if a specific component type is not present.
